  \begin{align*}
D(\Bun_{G,F_v},\La)^\om\ra^\sim D_{\coh}^{\qc}(\LS_{\prescript{L}{}{G},F_v})_{\Nilp}.
  \end{align*}
Consequently, applying $\Ind$ yields an equivalence
