            \item \label{wm:d=2_log_k}
            There exists $\phi$ solving \cref{in:eq:wave_map_k} with $d=2$ and $k\geq2$ s.t.~$\phi|_{\C}=\O\big(|\log(r)|^{\frac{-1}{2k-2}} \big)$ and s.t.~$\phi$ is smooth across $\C$ \cite{raphael_stable_2012}; 
